{"tid":1070090,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"日本足球文化點解咁熱血","createTime":"2019-03-20T11:35:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T16:52:50.000Z","uid":63482,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8313b73217f38c9c682dc3325f49b239cc3595f3","tid":1070090,"uid":63482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T11:35:03.000Z","msg":"今日收工覺得好頹，於是想搵啲令人會多正能量嘅片睇下，搵下搵下搵到條咁嘅紀錄片。雖然係蝗蝈片殘體字，但9成9時間都係講緊日文，睇到想喊，不過係好感動好熱血嗰種<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想分享下比大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n《少年足球養成》第三集- 願燃燒殆盡 登上夢想之地的終極一戰 <br />\n<br />\n係紀錄2018年嘅日本高中足球總決賽，見到球員同埋有老有嫩嘅應援團上下一心，由全國各地去到球場支持一間縣代表中學，真係好令人羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲有啲日本囡囡好cute<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nC4yllFL9lA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnC4yllFL9lA&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=13fa61d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nC4yllFL9lA</a><br />\n<br />\n當然，建議由第一集睇起<br />\n<br />\n《少年足球養成》第一集 - 全國制霸 一場銘記終身的足球教育課<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YI6mOzcnZc4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYI6mOzcnZc4&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=30c8ca81\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YI6mOzcnZc4</a><br />\n<br />\n《少年足球養成》第二集 - 青春的勳章 日本校園足夠OB文化<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jTSvhcKHwGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjTSvhcKHwGU&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=468c253f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jTSvhcKHwGU</a>"},{"pid":"a33c3bedacd5a55ef08d00fc8d825dafb73cfb3c","tid":1070090,"uid":187719,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T13:04:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dqApaRsDmyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.co